'''冈田谦三'''（{{jpn|j=岡田 謙三|kn=おかだ けんぞう}}，{{bd|1902年|9月28日|1982年|7月25日}}）是[[日本|日]]裔[[美国|美国]][[画家|画家]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://kotobank.jp/word/岡田%20謙三-1641036|title=岡田 謙三|date=|publisher=|accessdate=2021-01-03|author=Kotobank|language=ja|archive-date=2022-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220315021931/https://kotobank.jp/word/%E5%B2%A1%E7%94%B0%20%E8%AC%99%E4%B8%89-1641036}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://kotobank.jp/word/岡田謙三-39752|title=岡田謙三|publisher=Kotobank|accessdate=2021-01-03|language=ja|archive-date=2015-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150411070914/https://kotobank.jp/word/%E5%B2%A1%E7%94%B0%E8%AC%99%E4%B8%89-39752}}</ref>，生于[[神奈川县|神奈川县]][[横滨市|横滨市]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://www.spmoa.shizuoka.shizuoka.jp/_archive/collection/item/O_42_592_J.html|title=岡田 謙三|publisher=静岡県立美術館|accessdate=2021-01-03|language=JA|archive-date=2019-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190923183435/http://spmoa.shizuoka.shizuoka.jp/_archive/collection/item/O_42_592_J.html}}</ref>。他是[[抽象表现主義|抽象表现主義]]画家，以东方的“幽玄”绘画风格而闻名<ref name="eye of DP">The Phillips Collection. Ed. Erika D. Passantino. Consulting ed. David W. Scott. Researchers Virginia Speer Burden, ''The Eye of Duncan Phillips: A Collection in the Making'', Yale University Press, New Haven, 1999, {{ISBN|0300080905}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=ごあいさつ 岡田謙三展図録|url=https://www.bunka.pref.mie.lg.jp/art-museum/55680038753.htm|website=www.bunka.pref.mie.lg.jp|accessdate=2020-10-15|language=ja|archive-date=2020-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201017043811/https://www.bunka.pref.mie.lg.jp/art-museum/55680038753.htm}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=岡田謙三 :: 東文研アーカイブデータベース|url=https://www.tobunken.go.jp/materials/bukko/10133.html|website=www.tobunken.go.jp|accessdate=2020-10-15|archive-date=2020-10-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201018235404/https://www.tobunken.go.jp/materials/bukko/10133.html}}</ref>。曾在[[法国|法国]][[留学|留学]]<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=岡田謙三|url=